Configure game for telemetry

Usage: wheelctl game configure [OPTIONS] <GAME>

Arguments:
  <GAME>  Game ID

Options:
      --json         Output in JSON format for machine parsing
  -p, --path <PATH>  Game installation path
      --auto         Enable auto-configuration
  -v, --verbose...   Verbose logging
  -h, --help         Print help
